400
00:30:40,810 --> 00:30:43,080
Okay, naiintindihan ko. salamat po.

401
00:30:45,350 --> 00:30:47,020
Lalaking Kidlat! Tara na.

402
00:30:53,260 --> 00:30:55,060
Medyo nababaliw na ba ang lalaking iyon?

403
00:31:04,200 --> 00:31:06,000
Kailan natin makikita si Da Bong?

404
00:31:06,470 --> 00:31:07,800
Mamayang gabi.

405
00:31:09,770 --> 00:31:11,740
Pero gusto kong makipaglaro sa kanya ngayon.

406
00:31:15,580 --> 00:31:17,850
